<title>INDIA: India to introduce capital-indexed bonds.</title>
<headline>India to introduce capital-indexed bonds.</headline>
<dateline>NEW DELHI 1997-02-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>India plans to introduce capital-indexed bonds which would have principal repayments indexed to inflation, Finance Minister P. Chidambaram said on Friday.</p>
